{"tid":200389,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四驅車蝦學神　司機危駕判社服令","createTime":"2017-04-14T02:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T09:59:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2754e7b7744af6cc14a75ee9e4d462eb9f1103","tid":200389,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19989871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19989871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170414&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=89fbf388\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19989871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170414&h=4f54ad8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19989871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170414</a><br />\n<br />\n四驅車蝦學神　司機危駕判社服令<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告駕四驅車由停車場出車時，已緊貼電單車。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵路軌維修員年初駕駛四驅車時「大蝦細」，先從停車場出車時「過界」入路中央，逼近學牌電單車，之後多次推尾，最接近時相距一呎，最後更由左至右加速切線爬頭，學神要急煞避開，幸沒反車。惡行盡入後方私家車行車記錄儀，片段在網上瘋傳，私家車司機報警。四驅車司機早前承認一項危險駕駛罪，昨判社會服務令及停牌。<br />\n<br />\n罰停牌一年<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨引用案例指男被告羅國鈞（37歲）毋須判即時監禁。裁判官直言被告有意識地犯案，明知學牌司機駕駛經驗有限，四驅車亦比普通私家車「大咁多」，仍然犯案，以當時車速，有可能撞及電單車，不負責任程度高於同類案件；但考慮他已還柙兩周，判罰180小時社服令、停牌一年兼自費參加駕駛改進課程。<br />\n今年1月21日下午，被告由全輝中心停車場左轉崗背街，至過交通燈位右轉入沙角街期間犯案。警方3天後拘捕他。<br />\n案件編號：STCC741/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"44aded66d03f914b4ec97b5d626fa2120a3aa9e5","tid":200389,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"被告駕四驅車由停車場出車時，已緊貼電單車。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170414/large/14ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170414%2Flarge%2F14ls3p3.jpg&h=55320ab8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"435a5df0fdbd03c55d9f136d6d61872094f83d09","tid":200389,"uid":75235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"抵鳩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60433b3471701c84b02f6ba24922d8e1f6cf873","tid":200389,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f49049f65ebb441540089af058fb9d597f6aa9a","tid":200389,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"直頭瘋狂駕駛要停牌啦"},{"pid":"2f813c9c6af1809d4a4acf1c560cb848cd92f97c","tid":200389,"uid":51302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"6bb3eae9fce73049eb96372a6a3325c89adadacc","tid":200389,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"玩得咁撚過癮呀嗱  真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eb72670c1b3526f749c9d1ba70370d8e0b7f9d","tid":200389,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"452176c2aefd33f04dde088f3f423d9470a2dac4","tid":200389,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"根本危駕就判得過輕完全冇阻嚇性.<br />\n閒閒地判返一年監禁都唔過份,車死人判埋終身監禁先可以接受"},{"pid":"0b0cd0be5f522c5cc4e4252d93aec8fa1b2d8844","tid":200389,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"有冇片睇番？"},{"pid":"71ce76dfaa752f34cc15204dfa7952595b66e746","tid":200389,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩得咁撚過癮呀嗱  真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgm